      • attribute

        private final java.lang.String[] attribute
        String Array contain all data of the card/ football player. index: 0 - 7: basic information 0. name 1. nation 2.club 3.height 4. weight 5. foot 6. age 7. icon_path index: 8 - 12: 4 categories of abilities for comparison 8. attack 9. defence 10. skill 11. speed 12.power_capabilities
